<p itemprop="description">A lead infrastructure engineer provides strategic leadership for all infrastructure activities across the organisation. They establish enterprise-wide infrastructure strategies, drive innovation, and ensure alignment with business objectives and architectural principles.</p>

<section class="role-details">
    <h2>Typical responsibilities</h2>
    <ul>
        <li itemprop="responsibility">Provide strategic leadership for infrastructure across the organisation</li>
        <li itemprop="responsibility">Establish enterprise-wide infrastructure strategies and frameworks</li>
        <li itemprop="responsibility">Drive infrastructure innovation and emerging technology adoption</li>
        <li itemprop="responsibility">Lead digital transformation and cloud-first initiatives</li>
        <li itemprop="responsibility">Represent infrastructure interests in senior leadership forums</li>
        <li itemprop="responsibility">Develop strategic partnerships with cloud providers and technology vendors</li>
        <li itemprop="responsibility">Ensure alignment between infrastructure strategy and business objectives</li>
    </ul>
</section>

